[Oblivion Ring](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Oblivion Ring) is still far superior to this card. First of all, Oblivion Ring can target any nonland permanent (including Planeswalkers), not just creatures. Second, for an opponent to get his creature back, he has to take out the ring, not just pump his own creature.   

@gellar76:  
It seems that you are imagining that if the enchanted creature would be destroyed, destroy Ice Cage instead, which isn't the case at all. Ice Cage does nothing to protect creatures from removal. It is fragile removal in itself; nothing more.

